Cell[TextData[{
 "On a real QPU the same overlay would show the additional device noise, just \
as the IBM run did above. Running the IonQ task and reading back its ",
 Cell[BoxData["\"\<measurementProbabilities\>\""], "InlineFormula",
  ExpressionUUID->"30b72020-3e4b-4308-83f8-16b23a62a83b"],
 " gives the third bar to add to this chart."
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"f11f6d87-f226-4ee8-9841-2c5db171cda5"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

